        <main>
            <section>
                <h2>Transformative Journey</h2>
                <p>
                    Embark on a transformative journey of developing a practical .NET web-based application known as the
                    <strong>Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS)</strong>. This system serves as a crucial tool for streamlining
                    the often-complex process of submitting and approving monthly claims for independent contractor (iC) lecturers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    As a student in this module, you will dive deep into the development of .NET GUI development, leveraging
                    the power of C# to develop an interactive user interface and enhance the overall user experience for ICs.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Complex Calculations:</strong> The role of a lecturer extends beyond merely submitting claims; it involves complex calculations based on hours worked and corresponding hourly rates.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Thorough Scrutiny:</strong> Claims undergo thorough scrutiny by both the Programme Coordinator and the Academic Manager, highlighting the importance of accuracy and accountability in administrative processes.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Supporting Document Upload:</strong> The system integrates features that allow for seamless uploading of essential supporting documents, increasing efficiency and enhancing user satisfaction.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Learning Objectives</h2>
                <p>
                    Throughout your learning journey, you will explore various aspects of .NET GUI development, from designing visually appealing interfaces to implementing robust functionality. Each task or assessment will serve as a pivotal milestone, offering opportunities to apply theoretical knowledge to practical scenarios.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This POE not only equips you with the technical skills needed for GUI development but also instills a deeper understanding of the underlying principles driving modern software applications.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Future of Claim Management</h2>
                <p>
                    The Contract Monthly Claim System stands as a testament to innovation in administrative processes,
                    offering a glimpse into the future of streamlined claim management. By automating repetitive tasks and providing
                    intuitive interfaces, the system empowers both lecturers and administrators to focus on more strategic initiatives,
                    ultimately enhancing organizational efficiency and productivity.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Your Journey Begins!</h2>
                <p>
                    Through hands-on experience and guided instruction, you will emerge as a proficient C# developer, ready to tackle
                    real-world challenges in the dynamic landscape of software development.
                </p>
